    Format[edit]

    Qualifiers[edit]

    • 4 Server Qualifiers allow 11 players to qualify to the main events Group Stage.
      • 3 slots for the European server qualifier.
      • 3 slots for the American server qualifier.
      • 5 slots for the Korean server qualifiers (3 + 2).
    • Each Server Qualifier consists of an Open Qualifier and a Final Qualifier.
      • Open Qualifier
        • These qualifiers are open to all participants, with no region restrictions.
        • Single-elimination Bo3 until Round of 16.
        • Deciding matches Bo5.
        • Top 8 Advance to the Final Qualifier.
      • Final Qualifier
        • 8 players from the Open Qualifier and 8 seeded players.
        • Double-elimination Bo3.
        • Deciding matches Bo3.
        • 3 Players qualify to the main events Group Stage. (Via the second Korean server qualifier only 2 Players.)

    Round of 76[edit]

    • Held offline at the ESL Arena.
    • 64 players divided into 4 double-elimination brackets.
    • Top 3 players from each bracket advance to main tournament group stage.

    Round of 24[edit]

    • Group Stage:
      • Four groups of six players played out in round robin format.
      • All matches are Bo3.
      • First place in each group advances directly to the Quarterfinals.
      • Second and third place in each group advance to the Round of 12.
      • Ties broken in the following order [1]:
        1. Overall map difference
        2. Overall number of maps wins
        3. Points amassed between the tied participants
        4. Map difference between the tied participants
        5. Number of maps wins between the tied participants
    • Bracket:
      • Single-elimination bracket of twelve players.
      • Round of 12, Quarterfinals, and Semifinals are played in Bo5.
      • Grand Finals is played in Bo7.

    Prize Pool[edit]

    The base prize pool is $250,000 USD.
    In addition, it has been increased by a further $150,000 USD from War Chest purchases, totaling $400,000 USD in 2019.
    The winner is awarded a WCS Global Finals seed.
